      "role": "user",
      "content": "i found some really weird stuff in my grandfathers old trunk today. there is this heavy silver signet ring with a crest i've never seen before—it looks like a lion holding a broken scepter—and a bunch of old letters that mention a \"sovereign territory of Aethelgard\" that i can't find anywhere in any history books. i feel like i'm losing my mind but looking at the ring, it feels... ancient. like it actually belongs to someone important. can you help me figure out what this crest means or if Aethelgard was a real place that just got wiped from history?",
